From Michael Covington Subject Re Building a UV flashlight You can get a little UV by putting a heavy UV filter deep purple in front of an ordinary flashlight bulb the brightest you can get My father used a setup like this in law enforcement work circa Good UV blacklight bulbs work like fluorescent I'd proceed by getting a cheap battery powered fluorescent light then going to an electrical supply house and finding a UV bulb that would fit Michael Covington Associate Research Scientist Artificial Intelligence Programs The University of Georgia phone Athens Georgia amateur radio